devdoc.details: This library handles deposits to and withdrawals from dYdX liquidity pools.

deposit(uint256).details: Deposits funds to the dYdX pool. Assumes that you have already approved >= the amount to dYdX.

params.amount: The amount of ETH to be deposited.

getBalance().details: Returns the fund's balance in the KeeperDAO pool.

withdraw(uint256).details: Withdraws funds from the KeeperDAO pool.

params.amount: The amount of ETH to be withdrawn.

withdrawAll().details: Withdraws all funds from the KeeperDAO pool.
